      a: "<p>Eclipse supports a wide range of <strong>standard modifications</strong> â€” height changes, width adjustments, depth alterations â€” without requiring a custom quote. Watch the <a href='/dealer-hub/training-product-deep-dive'>Eclipse Standard Cabinet Modifications video</a> on the Product Deep-Dive page to learn what's available and which changes are standard vs. custom.</p>"
