      a: "<p>This is one of the most common errors. Vanities should be <strong>21â€³ depth</strong>, not 24â€³ (kitchen base depth). If the order hasn't been submitted yet, correct it in your design software. If already submitted, send corrections immediately to <a href='mailto:orders@wwinc.com'>orders@wwinc.com</a> â€” the sooner you catch it, the easier it is to fix before production begins.</p>"
    },
    {
      cat: "specs",
      q: "What is GOLA and which brand offers it?",
