    {
      cat: "specs",
      q: "What's the difference between framed (Shiloh) and frameless (Eclipse)?",
      a: "<p><strong>Framed cabinets (Shiloh)</strong> have a wood border around the cabinet opening â€” traditional look with visible frame between doors. <strong>Frameless cabinets (Eclipse)</strong> have doors that cover nearly the full cabinet face â€” sleek, contemporary European appearance with minimal gaps. Both use the same Â¾â€³ plywood construction. The choice is aesthetic, not quality. See the <a href='/dealer-hub/training-product-deep-dive'>Product Deep-Dive</a> for the full comparison.</p>"
    },
    // â€” Warranty & Claims â€”
    {
      cat: "warranty",
      q: "How do I report shipping damage?",
      a: "<p><strong>Inspect all cabinets upon delivery.</strong> Note any damage on the carrier's bill of lading before signing. Report damage or missing items to WW Wood Customer Service at 573-624-7090 <strong>within 5 business days</strong> of delivery. Include photos of damage, order number, and a completed warranty form. Download forms from the <a href='/dealer-hub/downloads'>Downloads & Forms</a> page.</p>"
