    {
      cat: "warranty",
      q: "Where do I find the warranty claim forms?",
      a: "<p>Download the brand-specific warranty form from the <a href='/dealer-hub/downloads'>Downloads & Forms</a> page or the <a href='/dealer-hub/ordering'>Ordering SOPs</a> page (Step 8). Forms are available for Shiloh, Eclipse, and Aspect. Watch the warranty request form walkthrough video to learn how to fill it out correctly.</p>"
